# Frontend Environment Variables

# API URL for the backend
# For local development: http://localhost:3001
# For production: your deployed backend URL (e.g., Vercel, Railway, etc.)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# 2. For production deployment, set VITE_API_URL to your deployed backend URL
# 3. GitHub Pages will use the environment variables you set in the repository settings